  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c4d2322ad35ce1344964dab582b54e74, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "So anyway, I found this underground website, ne? And it\u2019s like
    you can totally pay weird people to totally kill people for you. It\u2019s actually
    pretty cheap - Of course, you have to pay air-fare and everything since most
    of them are in baka countries SEA or Africa. \u2026And that\u2019s how I was
    able to find a pair of real super sentai chopsticks desu! Sugoi, ne? "
